author: pradine
msg: Changed the default for the wsa:ReplyTo header, in response messages, to the WSA none URI. This is the default for all response messages, except where a service has been deployed with soapsession scope. In this case the default is the WSA anonymous URI. The default for the wsa:ReplyTo header, in request messages, remains the WSA anonymous URI.
